<HEADLINE> Shanghai to Hold Int'l Food Trade Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 10 (Xinhua) -- China International Food Trade
Fair will be staged from August 28 to 30 this year in Shanghai,
the organizing committee announced here today.
</P>
<P>
The trade fair, with the goal of accelerating development of
China's food industry, will attract nearly 500 participants from
30 countries and regions, a committee official said.
</P>
<P>
The organizing committee will invite Chinese and foreign
experts to Shanghai on development of the food industry during the
trade fair.
</P>
<P>
The fair is co-sponsored China National Food Industry
Association and China Federation of Commerce.  
</P>
</TEXT>
