HAVANA, April 11 (Xinhua) -- Following is a statement by
visiting U.N. Secretary-General Kofi Annan, who Tuesday voiced his
warm welcome to the upcoming talks between leaders of South Korea
and the Democratic People's Republic of Korea:
</P>
