<HEADLINE> Algerian President to Visit France in June </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 11 (Xinhua) -- Algerian President Abdelaziz
Bouteflika will make a state visit to France from June 14 to 16,
Agence France-Presse quoted official sources as saying Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
