<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 11 (Xinhua) -- The impending four-day state
visit of Chinese President Jiang Zemin to Greece, the first ever
by a head of state of China to the Balkans, reflects China's
interest for stability and peace in the region.
</P>
