Chinese Vice President Hu Jintao told visiting Singapore Prime
Minister Goh Chok Tong here today that China hopes the two
countries will explore new ways and methods for enhancing
bilateral cooperation to push the Sino-Singaporean friendship and
relations of cooperation to a new phase.
</P>
<P>
