applied and its goals will be met, for the law will allow a
continuation of the strategy over several legislatures", he added.
</P>
<P>
The strategy is outlined jointly by the Agriculture Ministry, a
commission made up of cabinet members, experts designated by
parties, trade unions and employers unions.
</P>
<P>
In its nine chapters, analysis of the sector and perspectives
of joining the Europe Union are more heavily dealt with. 
