holidays from April 28 to May 6, with his first leg in Russia,
where he will hold an informal meeting with Russian President-
elect Vladimir Putin.
</P>
<P>
During his visit to France, Britain, Germany and Italy, Mori is
expected to hold talks with French President Jacques Chirac,
British Prime Minister Tony Blair, German Chancellor Gerhard
Schroeder and Italian Prime Minister Massimo D'Alema.
</P>
