<HEADLINE> People's Daily: Fallacy of Taiwan Independence (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The article counter-attacks her position, saying that Lu
overlooked one important factor: The change of regional leaders of
Taiwan does not alter the fact that the island is part of Chinese
territory.
</P>
