<HEADLINE> Jiangxi Deals Harshly With Police Breaching Law </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANCHANG, April 11 (Xinhua) -- Jiangxi Province, east China,
has punished policemen who broke the law in efforts to build a
cleaner police department.
</P>
<P>
