<HEADLINE> Overseas Funds Flow to Chinese Real Estate </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 11 (Xinhua)-- The number of overseas-funded real
estate enterprises has exceeded 5,000, accounting for 20 percent
of the country's total, said the Ministry of Construction.
</P>
<P>
Among the overseas-funded real estate enterprises, 3,800 are
from Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan investors.
</P>
<P>
