<TEXT>
<P>
ZHENGZHOU, April 11 (Xinhua) -- China will establish a project
reserve worth of 70 billion yuan (about 8.4 billion U.S. dollars)
in its central province of Henan to promote the construction of
infrastructure.
</P>
